01A324~&Cum variaza frecventa de rezonanta a unui circuit oscilant a carei inductanta se micsoreaza la jumatate si capacitatea se dubleaza?
null
frecventa de rezonanta se dubleaza
frecventa de rezonanta se injumatateste
frecventa de rezonanta se modifica exponential
frecventa de rezonanta ramane aceeasi
YO6GZI, Sacele, 2004
null
Formula lui Thomson: f<sub>0</sub> = 1/(2&pi;&radic;<span style="text-decoration:overline">L<sub>0</sub>C<sub>0</sub></span>)<br> Cu noile valori L<sub>1</sub> = L<sub>0</sub>/2 si C<sub>1</sub> = 2 * C<sub>0</sub> avem:<br>f<sub>1</sub> = 1/(2&pi;&radic;<span style="text-decoration:overline">L<sub>1</sub>C<sub>1</sub></span>) = 1/(2&pi;&radic;<span style="text-decoration:overline">(L<sub>0</sub>/2) * (2*C<sub>0</sub>)</span>) = 1/(2&pi;&radic;<span style="text-decoration:overline">L<sub>0</sub>C<sub>0</sub></span>) =  f<sub>0</sub><br>f<sub>1</sub> = f<sub>0</sub>, frecventa de rezonanta ramane aceeasi.
YO6OWN, Brasov, 2008
