null
In c.c. avem:<br>S = I<sub>A</sub>/U<sub>G</sub>;<br>Ri = 1/(I<sub>A</sub>/U<sub>A</sub>);<br>&micro;=U<sub>A</sub>/U<sub>G</sub>;<br>Inlocuind, avem Ri = 1/(S*U<sub>G</sub>/&micro;*U<sub>G</sub>) = &micro;/S deci &micro; = Ri * S = 3[V/mA] * 3[mA/V] = 9
YO6OWN, Brasov, 2008
