##244#
c
07A636~&20D63L/ Pe wattmetrul directional montat la intrarea in fiderul unui emitator se citesc: puterea in unda directa Pd= 100W si puterea in unda reflectata Pr=25w. Cat este raportul de unde stationare (SWR) in punctul de masura?
null
 SWR=100/25=4 
 SWR=&radic;<span style="text-decoration:overline">100/25</span> = &radic;<span style="text-decoration:overline">4</span> = 2
 &radic;<span style="text-decoration:overline">(25/100)</span> = &radic;<span style="text-decoration:overline">(1/4)</span> = 0,5; SWR=(1+0,5)/(1-0,5)=3
 25/100=0,25; SWR=(1+0,25)/(1-0,25)=1,66
Subiect public ANCOM, 2007
null
